    <briefdescription>
<para>Adds a constant offset to each element of a vector. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><preformatted>
    dst[n] = src[n] + offset,   0 &lt;= n &lt; block_size.
</preformatted> The functions support in-place computation allowing the source and destination pointers to reference the same memory buffer. There are separate functions for floating-point, Q7, Q15, and Q31 data types. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
